, \"to\": 906}, {\"ngram\": \"Britain'sgreatest-ever swimmer\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 938}, {\"ngram\": \"his own sporting ambitions\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 980}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The world record holder and three-timeOlympicchampion spent more thanhalf a decade as a god,even amongswimming's elite.\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1102, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The world record holder\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1006}, {\"ngram\": \"three-timeOlympicchampion\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1036}, {\"ngram\": \"more thanhalf\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1056}, {\"ngram\": \"a god\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"even amongswimming's elite\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1101}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after becoming the first British swimmer ever to retain anOlympictitle - doing so inthe 100m breaststroke in Tokyo- Peaty's invincibility has been brokenover the last three years.\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1132, \"end\": 1139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9852538873391455, \"rank\": 0.00834753301907184, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1216, \"end\": 1221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9997267003629755, \"rank\": 0.00027337412594620827, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"inthe 100m\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1199}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He suffered a first loss in his specialist event in eight yearsat the 2022 Commonwealth Games, and a combination of injury and abreak for mental health reasons,mean that he has missed three successive World Championships.\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1509, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a first loss\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1312}, {\"ngram\": \"his specialist event\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1336}, {\"ngram\": \"eight yearsat\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1353}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2022 Commonwealth Games\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1381}, {\"ngram\": \"a combination\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1400}, {\"ngram\": \"injury\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1410}, {\"ngram\": \"mental health reasons\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1447}, {\"ngram\": \"three successive World Championships\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1508}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His world record remains a distance clear of the field, but Peaty headsto Paris for his third Olympicsin an unfamiliar position.\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1639, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1585, \"end\": 1590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999489127744, \"rank\": 5.108700315601397e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His world record\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1565}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1576}, {\"ngram\": \"his third Olympicsin\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1615}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He might not quite be the underdog he claims, but he is no longer the overwhelming favourite.\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1733, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the underdog\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1674}, {\"ngram\": \"the overwhelming favourite\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1732}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the ultimate winner is happy with that position, having learned how to cope with defeat.\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1827, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ultimate winner\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1758}, {\"ngram\": \"that position\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1786}, {\"ngram\": \"defeat\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"Going into these Games, especially the last 12 months, I have enjoyed being the person with the bow and arrow and not the person being fired at.\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 1983, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1861}, {\"ngram\": \"the person\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1925}, {\"ngram\": \"the bow\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1938}, {\"ngram\": \"arrow\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1948}, {\"ngram\": \"the person\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 1967}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It gives you a different approach to it.\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 2024, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a different approach\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2017}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no real pressure on me.\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2057, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no real pressure\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yes, I am Olympic champion and people are going for that crown but anyone that follows the sport, will know I have not really raced, I have not really won anything since 2022 or 2021 but I am ok with that.\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic champion\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2086}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2097}, {\"ngram\": \"that crown\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2122}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2156}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2223}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am the underdog and I enjoy being the underdog, fighting my way through the ranks.\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2352, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the underdog\", \"from\": 2273, \"to\": 2285}, {\"ngram\": \"the underdog\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"my way\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2333}, {\"ngram\": \"the ranks\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If anything, it's shown me how to lose with grace.\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2403, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"grace\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before, I used to lose and I would tear everything up, I did not like it.\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2477, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2454}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been like that since I was a kid.\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2518, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a kid\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2517}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now, at 29 years old, I have learned how to lose.\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2570, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It does suck because I know how much I invest in myself and train and how much Team GB and Aquatics GB put in.\", \"from\": 2571, \"to\": 2681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2650, \"end\": 2657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999997221494, \"rank\": 2.7490139223135945e-10, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 2671, \"end\": 2673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9213943397765029, \"rank\": 0.08524585981340387, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We do not lose the ferocity, but you must bear in mind that you must lose sometimes to get these wins.\\\"\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2785, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ferocity\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2709}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2736}, {\"ngram\": \"these wins\", \"from\": 2773, \"to\": 2783}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty is one of over 1,000 elite athletes on UK Sport's National Lottery-funded World Class Programme, allowing them to train full time, have access to the world's best coaches and benefit from pioneering medical support - this is vital for his pathway to theParis 2024Games Peaty heads to Paris looking to match Michael Phelps and become only the second man to win gold in the same swimming event at three successive Olympics.\", \"from\": 2787, \"to\": 3215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2832, \"end\": 2840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 2832, \"end\": 2840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 3078, \"end\": 3083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999489127744, \"rank\": 5.108700315601397e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3101, \"end\": 3115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.483246855339012e-36, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 2787, \"to\": 2792}, {\"ngram\": \"over 1,000 elite athletes\", \"from\": 2803, \"to\": 2828}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 2929, \"to\": 2935}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's best coaches\", \"from\": 2939, \"to\": 2963}, {\"ngram\": \"medical support\", \"from\": 2992, \"to\": 3007}, {\"ngram\": \"his pathway\", \"from\": 3028, \"to\": 3039}, {\"ngram\": \"only the second man\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3145}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 3153, \"to\": 3157}, {\"ngram\": \"the same swimming event\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3184}, {\"ngram\": \"three successive Olympics\", \"from\": 3188, \"to\": 3213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And after three years in which he experienced some of his lowest ebbs, struggling with depression and alcohol problems, Peaty is at peace with himself.\", \"from\": 3217, \"to\": 3368, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three years\", \"from\": 3227, \"to\": 3238}, {\"ngram\": \"his lowest ebbs\", \"from\": 3271, \"to\": 3286}, {\"ngram\": \"depression and alcohol problems\", \"from\": 3304, \"to\": 3335}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 3337, \"to\": 3342}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 3349, \"to\": 3354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He explained: \\\"When you achieve what I have in the sport, Olympic golds, world records, that comes at a cost.\", \"from\": 3370, \"to\": 3479, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 3417, \"to\": 3426}, {\"ngram\": \"a cost\", \"from\": 3472, \"to\": 3478}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We all know that sport is extremely demanding.\", \"from\": 3480, \"to\": 3526, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 3497, \"to\": 3502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are continually learning as athletes and as people.\", \"from\": 3528, \"to\": 3583, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3560, \"to\": 3568}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3576, \"to\": 3582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport is very relatable to life because it is so, so tough.\", \"from\": 3584, \"to\": 3643, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sport\", \"from\": 3584, \"to\": 3589}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 3611, \"to\": 3615}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have those tough moments in your life where you must overcome them.\", \"from\": 3644, \"to\": 3715, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those tough moments\", \"from\": 3653, \"to\": 3672}, {\"ngram\": \"your life\", \"from\": 3676, \"to\": 3685}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the same in sport.\", \"from\": 3716, \"to\": 3739, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 3733, \"to\": 3738}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would not say it's a new me.\", \"from\": 3740, \"to\": 3770, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new me\", \"from\": 3761, \"to\": 3769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is still the deep chimp inside me who gets the job done, with a lot of anger.\", \"from\": 3771, \"to\": 3854, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the deep chimp\", \"from\": 3786, \"to\": 3800}, {\"ngram\": \"the job\", \"from\": 3820, \"to\": 3827}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3839, \"to\": 3844}, {\"ngram\": \"anger\", \"from\": 3848, \"to\": 3853}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there is also a new side of me which can process things a little bit more easily and consistently.\", \"from\": 3855, \"to\": 3957, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new side\", \"from\": 3873, \"to\": 3883}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 3908, \"to\": 3914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have had a lot of help from various people to help me get to that place.\", \"from\": 3958, \"to\": 4032, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3969, \"to\": 3974}, {\"ngram\": \"help\", \"from\": 3978, \"to\": 3982}, {\"ngram\": \"various people\", \"from\": 3988, \"to\": 4002}, {\"ngram\": \"that place\", \"from\": 4021, \"to\": 4031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This person now is going to carry on for the rest of my life.\", \"from\": 4034, \"to\": 4096, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This person\", \"from\": 4035, \"to\": 4046}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 4076, \"to\": 4084}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 4088, \"to\": 4095}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The one I had in Tokyo and Rio is not sustainable for the rest of your life because you cannot have that approach for everything.\", \"from\": 4097, \"to\": 4226, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4114, \"end\": 4119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9997267003629755, \"rank\": 0.00027337412594620827, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 4124, \"end\": 4127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9996929528524229, \"rank\": 0.0003071414543151554, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The one\", \"from\": 4097, \"to\": 4104}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 4151, \"to\": 4159}, {\"ngram\": \"your life\", \"from\": 4163, \"to\": 4172}, {\"ngram\": \"that approach\", \"from\": 4197, \"to\": 4210}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 4215, \"to\": 4225}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am more relaxed in my approach now, I am a bit more knowledgeable of self and I guess when I look at myself in the mirror, I am very peaceful.\", \"from\": 4228, \"to\": 4373, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my approach\", \"from\": 4250, \"to\": 4261}, {\"ngram\": \"self\", \"from\": 4300, \"to\": 4304}, {\"ngram\": \"the mirror\", \"from\": 4342, \"to\": 4352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As soon as you stop running from yourself, that is when you start living your true life.\", \"from\": 4374, \"to\": 4462, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your true life\", \"from\": 4447, \"to\": 4461}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In sport that is when you are most dangerous to everyone else.\", \"from\": 4463, \"to\": 4525, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 4466, \"to\": 4471}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 4511, \"to\": 4519}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not afraid to lose, I am not afraid to win.\", \"from\": 4526, \"to\": 4574, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How can you beat an athlete like that?\", \"from\": 4575, \"to\": 4613, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 4592, \"to\": 4602}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not control what anyone else does but I can stand behind the blocks and give it my best.\\\"\", \"from\": 4614, \"to\": 4709, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 4637, \"to\": 4643}, {\"ngram\": \"the blocks\", \"from\": 4677, \"to\": 4687}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The more sustainable Peaty is ready to accept that if his best is not enough this time, he will be able to lose with grace.\", \"from\": 4711, \"to\": 4834, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The more sustainable Peaty\", \"from\": 4711, \"to\": 4737}, {\"ngram\": \"grace\", \"from\": 4828, \"to\": 4833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Knowing Peaty, we might not find out.\", \"from\": 4835, \"to\": 4872, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 4843, \"to\": 4848}]}, {\"sentence\": \"National Lottery players raise more than \\u00a330million a week for good causes including vital funding into sport - from grassroots to elite.\", \"from\": 4874, \"to\": 5011, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4874, \"end\": 4890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"score\": 0.9999999897149792, \"rank\": 1.0284872744888355e-08, \"text\": \"National Lottery\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"good causes\", \"from\": 4937, \"to\": 4948}, {\"ngram\": \"vital funding\", \"from\": 4959, \"to\": 4972}, {\"